
Template: _APP_NAME_/mysql/standalone
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you want to install a new MySQL server locally?
 If you don't have a MySQL server already installed, choose this option to automatically install one of the local machine.

Template: _APP_NAME_/mysql/db_host
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: Host of your MySQL server
 Enter the IP or hostname of your MySQL server.

Template: _APP_NAME_/mysql/db_port
Type: string
Default: 3306
Description: Port of your MySQL server
 Enter the Port of your MySQL server.

Template: _APP_NAME_/mysql/db_username
Type: string
Description: Username used to connect to the MySQL server.
 Enter the username used to connect to your MySQL server.

Template: _APP_NAME_/mysql/db_password
Type: password
Description: Password used to connect to the MySQL server.
 Enter the password used to connect to your MySQL server.

Template: _APP_NAME_/mysql/db_name
Type: string
Description: Name of the database to use.
 Enter the name of the database to use. It must already be created on the MySQL server.
